{# Inline `{{ ... if ... }}` expressions on the body lines, NOT `{% if %}...{% endif %}`. The
   Environment uses trim_blocks=True which consumes the newline AFTER a block tag like {% endif %};
   if the {% endif %} is the last thing on a line, the per-iteration newline is eaten and bullets
   collapse onto one line. Inline {{ }} expressions don't consume the trailing newline.
